>\n警察失職，消防負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5671cec2f32eca93db84753f64aed79ed51b406e","tid":427360,"uid":125079,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:13:37.000Z","msg":"屯門河都跳得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  寧願坐監好過"},{"pid":"2c59f9b1c5eccc3ab3121462dbeac5a45b1f27f4","tid":427360,"uid":13065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"無牌賣酒又唔係販毒咁大單都走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最後實搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48a99366594a94550d1eac9a563b17896bd66ea","tid":427360,"uid":27381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無牌賣酒又唔係販毒咁大單都走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最後實搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵左成兩粒鐘啦 影都唔見"},{"pid":"d3289c33cec86caf20a679ab05403b7a584a19b7","tid":427360,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05528c45a7e1bd2083d50e10f1696834cc31e656","tid":427360,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"黑警走犯要消防埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人工仲要高過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef14f2f97d6e8d9abcee81ec808752d2f8547372","tid":427360,"uid":148074,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭輕鐵見到兩架消防<br />\n有蛙人落水 一開車門勁撚臭<br />\n見到啲警犬同救護係勁遠吹水<br />\n條友好似18唔太熟水性的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁臭都跳勇氣可加"},{"pid":"6d4301c4e0cbefb1f86108ac12d5845952f3c337","tid":427360,"uid":130247,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑警走犯要消防埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人工仲要高過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4vuwasbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4vuwasbg&h=6ed7020d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c51097ef3387d1e5a4d01086db03e552275dba73","tid":427360,"uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>15歲少年犯屯門警署逃走　跳河失蹤警搜尋中</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n屯門警署一名疑違反感化令的15歲少年，昨晚在無牌酒吧被警方無帶返屯門警署助查，揭發他欠交罰款，今晚7時許，其兄長帶錢到警署給他，詎料，少年突然逃離警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並跳入屯門河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，警員追至用手電筒照向河中搜索。據少年兄長透露，當時弟弟好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，突然開始跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用手「撳都撳唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n他尾隨胞弟至屯門河邊，見到胞弟已在河中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，警員不斷大聲叫他「返上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。期間，何游近岸邊5米位置，並聲稱腰痛，再有警署警長叫他上岸，惟少年卻掉頭游向河中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並失去蹤影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。兄長續稱：「佢唔識游水，好擔心其情況。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171007/photo/bkn-20171007200906400-1007_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171007203236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171007%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171007200906400-1007_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171007203236&h=50bd0534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 警員在河邊搜索。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171007/bkn-20171007200906400-1007_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171007%2Fbkn-20171007200906400-1007_00822_001.html&d=1MGcE3XRFIEMBMZtt5lJC7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=609fb899\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171007/bkn-20171007200906400-1007_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"66cce7d30253ac4e6c5ec22679379f020c41e004","tid":427360,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"完全無討論價值 成班都係文盲無知撚"},{"pid":"36bdc1bdba257d10198707fd269b80da86a3d7f3","tid":427360,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"驚超聯 all in 咗，今次fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b02a7ed58fd2960e0f0feca35d92cb78097c703","tid":427360,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全無討論價值 成班都係文盲無知撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0072b5c91f9fa3b53f6dacabd85a3d3c37a99648","tid":427360,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"屯門警署同屯門醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429af623d4e7b1df0e827a342a7ad245eb315fa3","tid":427360,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蛙人好慘 屯門條臭河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n消防局就喺隔離，可能即刻屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特別服務 警署走犯 細搶救車去屯門警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9962b4e7f1d076f59adace9edefff877f7b43","tid":427360,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"寧願臭死都唔願坐一頭半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1f8ee1f63f0b77b744b79bc8ef5fb3d5d6d804","tid":427360,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"有冇tuen mun人講下<br />\n如果佢keep住游會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f9a05d52047a3c6aa707d057b6f27e49ea469e","tid":427360,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"警犬四隻腳都跑得唔夠人快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb249a9da3bf3e28eecff7d896dc9fa42bb63b2","tid":427360,"uid":5159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"潛水怕屈機"},{"pid":"97f8f5a4a9b2eb03a7ceeab9b00eba94c93697a9","tid":427360,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"無牌賣酒好大獲咩, 洗唔洗咁博<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢有得保釋, 咪保釋先走都未遲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d070c70a97a71918eed45b2409f09f081036b0b4","tid":427360,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e4344fc963362bd41593eca5954377208d9a43","tid":427360,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"屯門警署走犯】18歲仔等候保釋時越柙 警海陸搜捕2小時<br />\n<br />\n【21:20】水警尋獲疑犯<br />\n<br />\n屯門警署發生走犯事件。一名18歲青年昨晚涉嫌無牌賣酒，被警方帶往屯門警署扣查。至今日晚上7時許，該名青年等候保釋期間，跨過報案室的大枱逃離警署。警員見狀尾隨追截，疑犯其後跳入屯門河逃去無蹤。大批警員正在屯門警署對開杯渡路橋底及V city一帶搜索。消防蛙人亦奉召到場，協助落屯門河搜捕在逃疑犯。<br />\n至晚上9時許，水警小艇於橋底尋獲疑犯，他雙手被扣上手銬，押返岸邊上岸。<br />\n<br />\n15歲定18歲呀"},{"pid":"5176b74d76970804a6d86eb613f1f4d68f150024","tid":427360,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門警署走犯】18歲仔等候保釋時越柙 警海陸搜捕2小時<br />\n<br />\n【21:20】水警尋獲疑犯<br />\n<br />\n屯門警署發生走犯事件。一名18歲青年昨晚涉嫌無牌賣酒，被警方帶往屯門警署扣查。至今日晚上7時許，該名青年等候保釋期間，跨過報案室的大枱逃離警署。警員見狀尾隨追截，疑犯其後跳入屯門河逃去無蹤。大批警員正在屯門警署對開杯渡路橋底及V city一帶搜索。消防蛙人亦奉召到場，協助落屯門河搜捕在逃疑犯。<br />\n至晚上9時許，水警小艇於橋底尋獲疑犯，他雙手被扣上手銬，押返岸邊上岸。<br />\n<br />\n15歲定18歲呀</blockquote><br />\n智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4165724a97ed8fcd17694d34ae8707d00157f7b2","tid":427360,"uid":24309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇tuen mun人講下<br />\n如果佢keep住游會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以睇下Google map<br />\n向南游可以出碼頭<br />\n不過重點係條河臭到出哂名"},{"pid":"ba558a4df486b35c681b93dc6750e55e5264caff","tid":427360,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇tuen mun人講下<br />\n如果佢keep住游會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以睇下Google map<br />\n向南游可以出碼頭<br />\n不過重點係條河臭到出哂名</blockquote><br />\n落左河已經死路<br />\n向工廠區走都無咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6547fb2cdb9e0cf238e6a93d405b962714beae","tid":427360,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"無牌賣酒都要走佬<br />\n身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a43a5069bfdbac285ac4356be9a395576e6358","tid":427360,"uid":63482,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇tuen mun人講下<br />\n如果佢keep住游會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以睇下Google map<br />\n向南游可以出碼頭<br />\n不過重點係條河臭到出哂名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條河近出海口（即係龍門居嗰邊）就冇咁臭既。<br />\n而西鐵站嗰邊就本來已經多渠口，再加埋呢啲天時又熱又冇乜雨呢，就好很臭。"},{"pid":"a81aa24f14019dd033512ba1710375b1c38502ab","tid":427360,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b350e911cab9c03260603f96b43234ef2c1fdfe","tid":427360,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧願臭死都唔願坐一頭半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d濕鳩碎罪都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617ef9230390e5d2e64f042ff97777f073796ce7","tid":427360,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"痴線條河臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bd515044b10fc09a97a3738c786eeee509de58","tid":427360,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"香港警柒"},{"pid":"393fdde653eca63ddc475682df1ab954633d102c","tid":427360,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"屯門全港第一<br />\n又有得j"},{"pid":"6e3a17987b0b50566f7c452ff93a1fd314081d71","tid":427360,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門警署走犯】18歲仔等候保釋時越柙 警海陸搜捕2小時<br />\n<br />\n【21:20】水警尋獲疑犯<br />\n<br />\n屯門警署發生走犯事件。一名18歲青年昨晚涉嫌無牌賣酒，被警方帶往屯門警署扣查。至今日晚上7時許，該名青年等候保釋期間，跨過報案室的大枱逃離警署。警員見狀尾隨追截，疑犯其後跳入屯門河逃去無蹤。大批警員正在屯門警署對開杯渡路橋底及V city一帶搜索。消防蛙人亦奉召到場，協助落屯門河搜捕在逃疑犯。<br />\n至晚上9時許，水警小艇於橋底尋獲疑犯，他雙手被扣上手銬，押返岸邊上岸。<br />\n<br />\n15歲定18歲呀</blockquote><br />\n衰多一次罪，坐硬"},{"pid":"0233a38cb625daf13b59b354dc25f331db2ac12f","tid":427360,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇tuen mun人講下<br />\n如果佢keep住游會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一面係龍門居/碼頭，另一面屯門醫院/兆康/藍地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d061d8d4f0ed52d4269676e51f97c91676f10976","tid":427360,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"260bc298031f7852a557e631480e2529bf56c983","tid":427360,"uid":10992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"冇lun 用"},{"pid":"813fd0b5a6bdeb5dbf5bc466eeb496ae8d16ac9a","tid":427360,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"班警犬以為做緊亡命天涯呀派蛙人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfce9324e16a746e72ade42a6768bd081756e4fd","tid":427360,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"on9 走得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d924aa272dc79d9cf51809337d27b8d3f856726f","tid":427360,"uid":40644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:56:49.000Z","msg":"係咪on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  保釋緊都要走"},{"pid":"e9ec3b3b7cb0adf985c5636ada93b147111124b3","tid":427360,"uid":27492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"條河真係臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cbc9c4cbf12d8a5272059a4bb0ab17c7c3bdcc","tid":427360,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屯門警署發生走犯事件。一名20歲青年昨晚涉嫌無牌賣酒，被警方帶往屯門警署扣查。至今日晚上7時許，<span style=\"color: red;\">該名青年等候保釋期間，突然逃離警署</span>。警員見狀尾隨追截，疑犯其後逃去無蹤。大批警員正在屯門警署對開杯渡路橋底及V city一帶搜索。<span style=\"color: red;\">消防蛙人亦奉召到場，協助落屯門河搜捕在逃疑犯</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蛙人陰公</blockquote><br />\n消防:屌你老母我救人架，走犯關我撚事咩</blockquote><br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人工仲要低過黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95cbf084db812f23b8770a9dbde2fcc9b20a659","tid":427360,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"協助落屯門河搜捕在逃疑犯<br />\n<br />\n黑人問號"},{"pid":"aec3969bcdcdacd28d21894c867e2951b4fe06e0","tid":427360,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3dfc143e6bc477002c8a72feb301ccab0053c44","tid":427360,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"18歲入沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0f3202626987a1c4d0675b4674486fa85f3995","tid":427360,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"點解等緊保釋都要逃走？"},{"pid":"0783f3dab600bdaf2a1615abd88af312c1b3567b","t